            στεροπῆς,</span>
          <i><span class="en">Il. 19.362</span></i>; <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">
            ἐμὸν δ᾽ ἐγέλασσε φίλον κῆρ</span>, ‘laughed within me,’ <i><span class="en">Od. 9.413</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
